By: Plotinus
---
Harmonies unheard create the harmonies we hear and wake the soul to the
consciousness of beauty, showing it the one essence in another kind; for the
measures of our music are not arbitrary, but are determined by the Principle
whose labor is to dominate matter and bring pattern into being.
